    "attributes": {
      "name": "Virtual Piano",
      "summary": "A card component that presents an interactive, full-featured virtual piano with capabilities including playback of VP.net notation, multi-instrument sound profiles, real-time recording and playback, and keyboard/mouse interaction. It provides a user interface for song selection, auto-play, transposition, and sound settings, along with notation visualization. The component supports VP.net notation parsing, multi-instrument sound synthesis, and precise scheduling for autoplay, enabling users to simulate piano play, record performances, and explore sheet music within a web-based environment.",
